{{Quote|What, impossible. You were restrained by a neural disruptor!|Brejik|<ref name="Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]''</ref>}}
'''Neural disruptors''' were devices similar to collars attached to [[Prisoner/Legends|prisoners]]' necks to incapacitate them. [[Brejik]] used this device on [[Bastila Shan]], only to be outwitted by the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]], who managed to resist it and take it off with help from [[The Force/Legends|the Force]].

